          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Excelencia</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Buscamos la perfección en cada entrenamiento y competición, 
              siempre con el objetivo de alcanzar el máximo rendimiento.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 100-5H9m0 0H5.5a2.5 2.5 0 100 5H9m-4 4v2a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-2"/>
